'''Angela Kyerematen-Jimoh''' is a Ghanaian business leader. She is currently the Country General Manager for [[IBM]] Ghana.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ghananewsagency.org/social/ibm-appoints-new-country-manager--91361|title=IBM appoints new Country Manager|access-date=2018-02-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gipcghana.com/press-and-media/427-big-data-big-opportunity-for-ghana-ibm-boss.html|title=Big Data, Big Opportunity For Ghana - IBM Boss - Ghana Investment Promotion Centre (GIPC)|website=www.gipcghana.com|language=en-gb|access-date=2018-02-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://citifmonline.com/2015/07/03/ibm-appoints-new-country-general-manger-for-ghana/angela-kyerematen-jimoh-country-gm-ibm-ghana/|title=Angela Kyerematen-Jimoh (Country GM, IBM Ghana) - Ghana News|work=Ghana News|access-date=2018-02-20|language=en-US}}</ref> She is the first female to become country director of [[IBM]] in Africa.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.modernghana.com/news/802767/ibm-ghana-ceo-angela-kyerematen-jimoh-receives-womanrising.html|title=IBM Ghana CEO, Angela Kyerematen-Jimoh Receives WomanRising Award|last=Akpah|first=Prince|work=Modern Ghana|access-date=2018-02-20|language=en-gb}}</ref>
== Education == Angela holds a BA in Marketing and French. She is a graduate of [[Harvard Business School]] in Leadership Development.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.biztechafrica.com/article/angela-kyerematen-jimoh-heads-ibm-ghana-country-ge/10313/|title=Angela Kyerematen-Jimoh heads IBM Ghana as Country General Manager|work=BiztechAfrica|access-date=2018-02-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://newsdog.today/a/article/5a40997212313a18d9e32fc8/?d=false|title=Powerful CEOs: The most stylish female Ghanaian CEOs of 2017 - NewsDog|access-date=2018-02-21}}</ref>
== Career == She has 15 years extensive working experience in the financial services and technology industries in Africa and Europe. In 2011 she joined IBM as the Territory Marketing Manager responsible for IBM West Africa. She later moved to [[Nairobi]], [[Kenya]] as Strategy Leader for IBM’s Central, East and West Africa operations.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ghananewsagency.org/social/ibm-appoints-new-country-manager--91361|title=IBM appoints new Country Manager|access-date=2018-02-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://citibusinessnews.com/index.php/2015/07/03/ibm-appoints-new-country-general-manger-for-ghana/|title=IBM appoints new Country General Manger for Ghana - Ghana Business News|date=2015-07-03|work=Ghana Business News|access-date=2018-02-20|language=en-US}}</ref>
== Awards == WomenRising ranked her among the Top 50 Corporate Women Leaders in [[Ghana]] for 2016.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.modernghana.com/news/802767/ibm-ghana-ceo-angela-kyerematen-jimoh-receives-womanrising.html|title=IBM Ghana CEO, Angela Kyerematen-Jimoh Receives WomanRising Award|last=Akpah|first=Prince|work=Modern Ghana|access-date=2018-02-20|language=en-gb}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/business/Google-Ghana-CEO-receives-top-corporate-women-leaders-award-591388|title=Google Ghana CEO receives top corporate women leaders award|website=www.ghanaweb.com|language=en|access-date=2018-02-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://newsofthesouth.com/ibm-ghana-ceo-angela-kyerematen-jimoh-receives-womanrising-award/|title=IBM Ghana CEO Angela Kyerematen- Jimoh Receives WOmanRising Award {{!}} News of the South|website=newsofthesouth.com|language=en|access-date=2018-02-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://article.wn.com/view/2017/09/15/IBM_Ghana_CEO_Angela_KyerematenJimoh_Receives_WomanRising_Aw/|title=IBM Ghana CEO, Angela Kyerematen-Jimoh Receives WomanRising Award|website=article.wn.com|language=en|access-date=2018-02-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.peacefmonline.com/pages/business/news/201610/294023.php|title=Top 50 Women Corporate Leaders in Ghana|last=Online|first=Peace FM|access-date=2018-02-20}}</ref>
