{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2014}} {{Use New Zealand English|date=December 2014}} {{Distinguish|Jack Hazlitt|John Hazlitt}} {{Infobox rugby biography | name = Jack Hazlett | image = Jack Hazlett.jpg | image_size = 240px | caption = | nickname = | birth_name = Edward John Hazlett | birth_date = {{Birth date|1938|07|21|df=yes}} | birth_place = [[Invercargill]], New Zealand | death_place = Invercargill, New Zealand | death_date = {{Death date and age|2014|12|16|1938|07|21|df=yes}} | ru_position = [[Rugby union positions#Prop|Prop]] | height = {{convert|1.88|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}} | weight = {{convert|95|kg|lb|abbr=on}} | allblackid = 371 | allblackno = 654 | ru_nationalteam = {{nowrap|{{ru|New Zealand}}}} | ru_nationalyears = 1966–67 | ru_nationalcaps = 6 | ru_nationalpoints = (0) | ru_province = [[Southland Rugby Football Union|Southland]] | ru_provinceyears = 1960–68 | ru_provincecaps = 87 | ru_provincepoints = | occupation = | family = | spouse = | children = | relatives = [[William Edgar Hazlett|Bill Hazlett]] (uncle) | school = [[Christ's College, Christchurch|Christ's College]] | university = }}
'''Edward John "Jack" Hazlett''' {{post-nominals|country=NZL|MNZM|size=85%}} (21 July 1938 – 16 December 2014) was a New Zealand [[rugby union]] player. A [[Rugby union positions#Prop|prop]], Hazlett represented [[Southland Rugby Football Union|Southland]] at a provincial level, and was a member of the New Zealand national side, the [[All Blacks]], in 1966 and 1967. He played 12 matches for the All Blacks including six internationals.<ref>{{cite web| url = http://stats.allblacks.com/asp/Profile.asp?ABID=371 |title = Jack Hazlett | last = Knight | first = Lindsay | publisher = New Zealand Rugby Union | accessdate = 22 December 2014}}</ref>
Hazlett went on to establish Slinkskins Ltd, a Southland-based tanning company, in 1968,<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.slinkskins.co.nz |title=Slinkskins Ltd |date= |website= |publisher= |accessdate=22 December 2014}}</ref> and in the [[1996 Birthday Honours|1996 Queen's Birthday Honours]] he was appointed a [[New Zealand Order of Merit|Member of the New Zealand Order of Merit]] for services to export.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dpmc.govt.nz/node/1025 |title=Queen's Birthday honours list 1996 |date=3 June 1996 |publisher=Department of the Prime Minister and Cabinet |accessdate=22 December 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160719214125/http://www.dpmc.govt.nz/node/1025 |archivedate=19 July 2016 |df=dmy-all }}</ref>
